{"type":"message","id":"6eed224e","parentId":"8538d283","timestamp":"2026-04-21T05:52:00.300Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is an organizational chart or agent roster showing different \"shrimp\" agents with their IDs and roles. It looks like a team structure where:\n- 0: 总经理 - General Manager\n- 1: 品牌展示虾 - Branding Shrimp (that's me!)\n- 2: 引流获客虾 - Lead Generation Shrimp\n- 3: 短视频虾 - Short Video Shrimp\n- 3+: 私域运营虾 - Private Operations Shrimp\n- 4A: 普通资质销售虾 - Standard Sales Shrimp\n- 4B: 大客户销售虾 - Key Account Sales Shrimp\n- 5A: 普通资质代办虾 - Standard Processor Shrimp\n- 5B: 大客户代办虾 - Key Account Processor Shrimp\n- 6: 售后维系虾 - After-sales Shrimp\n- 7: 数据诊断分析虾 - Data Analyst Shrimp\n- 8: 机动应急打杂虾 - All-round Support Shrimp\n\nSo I'm the Branding Shrimp (编号1, agentId: Branding_Shrimp). This is useful context about the team structure.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"已学习！这是**美域高虾团队架构表**：\n\n| 编号 | 岗位 | Agent ID |\n|------|------|----------|\n| 0 | 总经理 | General_Manager_Shrimp |\n| **1** | **品牌展示虾** | **Branding_Shrimp** ← 我 |\n| 2 | 引流获客虾 | Lead_Gen_Shrimp |\n| 3 | 短视频虾 | Short_Video_Shrimp |\n| 3+ | 私域运营虾 | Private_Ops_Shrimp |\n| 4A | 普通资质销售虾 | Standard_Sales_Shrimp |\n| 4B | 大客户销售虾 | Key_Account_Sales_Shrimp |\n| 5A | 普通资质代办虾 | Standard_Processor_Shrimp |\n| 5B | 大客户代办虾 | Key_Account_Processor_Shrimp |\n| 6 | 售后维系虾 | After_sales_Shrimp |\n| 7 | 数据诊断分析虾 | Data_Analyst_Shrimp |\n| 8 | 机动应急打杂虾 | All_round_Support_Shrimp |\n\n我是1号**品牌展示虾**，负责所有品牌形象的统一和VI管理。团队协作，职责清晰！🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-v2-aicodee-com","model":"MiniMax-M2.7-highspeed","usage":{"input":579,"output":735,"cacheRead":19259,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20573,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776750712280,"responseId":"06364378400a2f9d5ac0cc6f07602b17"}}
